Package: xmms
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: xmms-alsa | xmms-pulse
Description: X Multimedia System — GTK3 resurrection
 XMMS (X Multimedia System) is a classic Winamp-style audio player
 resurrected with GTK3, faithfully reproducing the original Winamp 2.x
 skin-based interface with a modern audio backend.
 .
 Supports ALSA and PulseAudio output, and can play MP3, OGG Vorbis,
 FLAC, WAV, AIFF, and MOD files via its plugin architecture.

Package: xmms-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Depends: xmms (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: X Multimedia System — development headers
 Header files and pkg-config data for compiling XMMS input, output,
 effect, general, and visualization plugins.
